      <title>诺博亚宣布紧急状态后，厄瓜多尔暴力事件激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/ecuador-suffers-surge-of-violence-after-noboa-declares-emergency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺博亚在追捕臭名昭著的毒枭期间宣布进入紧急状态，在全国范围内实行宵禁，之后一夜之间再次发生暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/ecuador-suffers-surge-of-violence-after-noboa-declares-emergency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 15:46:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普律师辩称选举案使前任总统面临刑事指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-lawyers-argue-election-prosecution-opens-pandora-s-box</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师告诉联邦上诉法院小组，因试图推翻 2020 年大选而起诉唐纳德·特朗普引发了人们的疑问，即其他前任总统是否可能因官方行为而受到刑事指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-lawyers-argue-election-prosecution-opens-pandora-s-box</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 15:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数千人失去热量后普京将国防工厂国有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/putin-to-nationalize-defense-plant-after-thousands-lost-heat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫斯科附近地区州长称，该工厂在寒冷天气下引发供暖故障，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京下令将一家生产弹药的国防工厂国有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/putin-to-nationalize-defense-plant-after-thousands-lost-heat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫召集气候顾问讨论液化天然气出口审批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/white-house-assembles-climate-advisers-on-lng-export-approvals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，拜登政府正在重新评估其在批准新的液化天然气出口设施时使用的气候标准，此举可能会随着 2024 年大选的临近而导致悬而未决的项目陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/white-house-assembles-climate-advisers-on-lng-export-approvals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:46:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>到 2050 年，大电池可为英国电力系统节省高达 240 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/big-batteries-may-save-uk-power-system-up-to-24-billion-by-2050</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顾问公司 LCP Delta 表示，随着英国在推动海上风电扩张的过程中寻求可靠的备用电源，长期储能可以为英国电力系统节省数十亿英镑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/big-batteries-may-save-uk-power-system-up-to-24-billion-by-2050</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
