    <item>
      <title>马克龙任命加布里埃尔·阿塔尔为法国最年轻总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/france-s-macron-taps-34-year-old-ally-attal-as-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离欧洲议会选举仅几个月，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命一位 34 岁的盟友为法国总理，为他的政府带来新的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/france-s-macron-taps-34-year-old-ally-attal-as-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:23:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共同被告声称特朗普检察官有不正当恋情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-prosecutor-had-improper-relationship-co-defendant-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法庭文件中称，亚特兰大地区检察官法尼·威利斯 (Fani Willis) 不当聘请了一名浪漫伴侣，帮助起诉针对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 和其他 18 人的选举舞弊指控，后者是前总统的共同被告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-prosecutor-had-improper-relationship-co-defendant-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:12:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望美国市场崩盘发生在拜登领导下，而不是他本人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-hopes-any-us-market-crash-happens-under-biden-and-not-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他希望美国经济崩溃发生在今年，而不是在他预期的第二任期内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/trump-hopes-any-us-market-crash-happens-under-biden-and-not-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 03:29:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索马里领导人警告他将反对埃塞俄比亚红海计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/somalia-leader-warns-he-will-fight-against-ethiopia-red-sea-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索马里总统警告说，如果邻国埃塞俄比亚采取进一步措施确保通过索马里兰（索马里的一个分离地区）直接进入红海，他将采取“一切必要措施”保卫国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/somalia-leader-warns-he-will-fight-against-ethiopia-red-sea-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 13:56:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
